xSeRYcUk\" alt=\"竹內涼真（IG@takeuchi_ryoma）\"><figcaption>竹內涼真（IG@takeuchi_ryoma）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20241027/927244697628315648952710.jpeg/sp9f1qXn1F30XfeciLMEiwX24obkWazljGB5XoxgeV4\" alt=\"竹內涼真（IG@takeuchi_ryoma）\"><figcaption>竹內涼真（IG@takeuchi_ryoma）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20241027/927244699905953792387612.jpeg/Yk5-BMUFvhBG7E8YYyg-X4tH8IJ3KzQ2O44a_juOGv4\" alt=\"竹內涼真（IG@takeuchi_ryoma）\"><figcaption>竹內涼真（IG@takeuchi_ryoma）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20241027/927244702204563456410672.jpeg/gdU6M9Pqc1nptFhl9Io6Fk6ZMQi_07fyx3d3UMd3d1A\" alt=\"竹內涼真（IG@takeuchi_ryoma）\"><figcaption>竹內涼真（IG@takeuchi_ryoma）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20220708/622113780051087360754930.png/fMAK8zMdelC2Nv0Q7IxnV-tWhr3DTE_8GL-Txxi_k8c\" alt=\"竹內涼真（IG@takeuchi_ryoma）\"><figcaption>竹內涼真（IG@takeuchi_ryoma）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20220708/622113769103429632670538.png/E_hTiUB8_SAnCOO-kYla1AuDt1MSlf6CfrqA6H66gOg\" alt=\"竹內涼真（IG@takeuchi_ryoma）\"><figcaption>竹內涼真（IG@takeuchi_ryoma）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4146855/org/66d33ac022e7d58ede77cc826d080535.png/cTDI5iTA-L2FHiyPfWfcfEEgDMPGbwYeTMtc3EzLXNw\" alt=\"竹內涼真（《Black Pean 黑色止血鉗》劇照）\"><figcaption>竹內涼真（《Black Pean 黑色止血鉗》劇照）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4146856/org/44fdc7a8d0dcf5d851ab571ffc22da4d.png/o4RYSH4r5ygsxAxflHHdQwQTLm8HKKOVCi9YUQovWFE\" alt=\"竹內涼真（《Black Pean 黑色止血鉗》劇照）\"><figcaption>竹內涼真（《Black Pean 黑色止血鉗》劇照）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e0083b0fd5cc31c9c2b659b.jpeg/Yb3GBucIDtFr1IpVcMlhX9ry5p6Rmt2YtEEKrrRBCq4\" alt=\"竹內涼真（IG@takeuchi_ryoma）\"><figcaption>竹內涼真（IG@takeuchi_ryoma）</figcaption></figure><p>延伸閱讀：</p><p>元元玩股票「半個月淨賺100萬」震撼全場！資深藝人慘賠500萬崩潰：我們到底在幹嘛</p><p>華晨宇讓貓舔巧克力影片瘋傳！遭轟無知：想害死貓？</p><p>【本文獲「聯合新聞網」授權轉載。】</p></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-22T17:05:11.500786+00:00","quality":{"score":3,"chars":2144,"images":46,"source":"HK01 娛樂","fallback":"none"}}